ree Spot Exchange and Derivative Protocol](https://mirror.xyz/0x76FF0594486eA591E6B8955d703b02Ec5cEBc55F/CNvtK0VGDymJaSNSJZgtbEE2iHsroZ9ixMYC2P6N7LE)：衍生品协议Primitive概述，可结合Primitive发表在Mirror上的[文章](https://mirror.xyz/0x801D5e44960C5934181B04290Ec7F6A27d96cFF1/l5F1BLMhfmcm_B1R2w-by003_oiAz2-Ir_Jj_rCvGCs)阅读。\\n* [Socios.com- Its more than a game , Be more than a fan !](https://mirror.xyz/0x21EBf7E058D93BBe9e6aC5d9Fae3aC10ACA036Ff/YAkCEiVn0tLsk6UjS71LVEyLwy5uJSqPsMZMjE4yD6Q)：介绍体育类粉丝代币平台Socios。\\n* [Web3 Interoperability: The Hard Parts](https://mirror.xyz/0xf548E23535Dfb903aeaEEaAaF3be6847Fe4791CE/5hF6CioiOdk87S5mhwIUHpTgINmaNwibgY73YFpU2vg)：描绘三层组合金字塔，底层是诸如以太坊等公链的语义组合，中间层是诸如ERC721等标准的接口组合，顶层是消费者导向的产品组合。\\n* [Taming the Stablecoin Beast: An analysis on stablecoins, their use cases and benefits, and potential avenues for regulation](https://mirror.xyz/0x8BE2355417EF645f3A3739DD1B8aBd38C563c595/I_YVezBT2phoesGubpmWtBZWComtqaBDmtFTgLVEDcY)：稳定币爱好者的福音，详细分析稳定币及用例、监管等。\\n* [Elimy's 2022 NFT Picks](https://mirror.xyz/0x168b9Bd22F3951466b32c0b31639E933d2b0FCce/eT3d0_IwTunt9gBW-_pq3AbWUOcmIF8lh0XwHuXO_Ek)：作者按照价格筛选了一些自己喜欢的NFT项目。\\n* [web3.GSEA: 2021 Greater Southeast Asia Web3 Ecosystem Map](https://mirror.xyz/0x5A7E8e7A128BFD0aaE264335880e6C969E31beeE/E-28Trbzn-qDKvLQHTtducPinjSGv0wE-o0b7Paf9Lk)：分析东南亚各国的加密市场环境、特点及其代表性项目。\\n\\n### 教育教学\\n\\n* [How did content marketing come about and what is its importance for my brand as a writer.](https://mirror.xyz/0xab210e2600C72E26f0e38D43D71a551aA8494EC4/nZLy04_XuUwMAUST_caPgKaYy4G2KPZwGRm0dHGpXT4)：介绍内容营销的历史，内容营销对作者成功很重要。小编注：论一个没有内容营销的周报精选内容营销文章时的感受。\\n* [Create your own token without code using thirdweb](https://mirror.xyz/0xDd3C87Cb8513812be41A8829b8af87577313484E/HGL6XOknXUyENNxABa_5S-6zBXBEf5iYGDoC-l-tht4)：使用Thirdweb，无需编程即可自行创建代币。\\n* [Tapping into DAO Ecology](https://thedaoist.mirror.xyz/8jKbVJCJgUFk5BT6RqE4UjGcWY3Qjr1ZnzVZVnvurIc)：主要介绍DAO的生态，互动和协作的 DAO 生态系统，DAO2DAO的概念及应用。贡献者：Stella-s🐰#4484\\n* [How Phuture works?– Non-technical overview & Guide to create your index.](https://mirror.xyz/0x4C97d594e0a39A731E7820610bC8fce068Ede5d8/Sg7mOYOK1yrRxc_T61b_nsbGpMwO0Z6ZlfINbYq86p4)：介绍资产管理平台Phuture，以及教你如何成为指数基金经理。\\n* [Three gas saving tips on ethereum](https://mirror.xyz/0x56383A5Dd01d413fb8B38F2D0FceF5F511F1Dbb9/m4henCen0umuKpf5o9R-AlaTHXdePo9kwV__P2-HhwQ)：三个省gas费小技巧：使用gas追踪工具合理设置gas费；替换交易而不是取消待确认交易；配置flashbot RPC来避免失败和还原的交易。\\n\\n### 思考\\n\\n* [The NFT Code for Creators](https://mirror.xyz/0x296652d97B7caF5924f8E267195Aedd1bd846d80/Mx2pFCh3pBRndkUrSywg-fbNPS2ad5NQYwAo2DPFwN0)：创作者的NFT行为规范。\\n* [Why I care about artist-owned contracts and storefronts](https://mirror.xyz/0xb27b3CD0EfD8F70257CEC812Ea4330670C4D4fc5/Ba-cBZsfpAFU-JyzGJDbOpA0TM0_9Xa7anpCfRBAceE)：18+ NFT创作者的控诉。\\n* [Why Web3 Matters & 10 People I Want to Talk to in 2022](https://mirror.xyz/0xFC965f2075077Ee54B59aFb3B16780C1Cba0d22F/V2qAqa3IdBWHBw2Ls6FVPa2uDzNin3RRNWYxQNqRYLQ)：先奶一波Web3的重要性及意义，然后列举十位作者想在2022年对话的人物。小编注：想对话的大部分是名人，而我们则更喜欢关注普通人。\\n* [Looking Onward for Crypto Gaming](https://mirror.xyz/0x6477F082eD179739B9c6Bc982ed946E99114b46E/FQa1LIPeWnaQ_mkJbyZJuAyi7fCjoPNBpLWoCP3y4hY)：哈佛大学区块链俱乐部出品的链游全览。小编注：超长慎点。\\n* [Identity & inclusion in web3](https://society.mirror.xyz/qP9cHZfIQVxCyzy1EYdbQm73RinStYfObxvoh7SgJ9w)：CCS与Dame就身份与包容性的谈话总结。\\n\\n### 经历经验\\n\\n* [Who is Jade Kats?](https://mirror.xyz/0x19de52Bc6207f8dc7633dBD66FE2936eAB713868/gp05zFidqaPEugnVyomEBhfvq5BhR6poi6AENmQg2NM)：投入诸多时间、精力到一个非营利性项目，然后将其转换成可以变现的DAO的故事。\\n* [Vitalik in Argentina](https://mirror.xyz/0x86aa399A62b6D89f4d6306c82656bE29CB2E728A/7hmYRIBZrxIkNd1wfoUsXvgisQG70k2p7FSFOUj3CvI)：币圈追星的力量。\\n* [A journey through web3: decentralized sites and applications](https://mirror.xyz/timnotjim.eth/LPfoY8-tcM7EtXty4YuRkR6q4WbtbF31YmyaNwTYAFs)：介绍Web3用到的一些网站和应用。\\n* [Metaverse Carnival 2021 Panel Recap | How Identities are Core to Web3](https://mirror.xyz/0xd8159c4DD43FEe99FA86D0BAaCA7a9cC33334864/-yMZyd-mqnyWC1n1lbAJnRM-XuSIjMKN7l1lVL5R7BI)：IOSG老友会中一场关于身份讨论的圆桌论坛。\\n\\n# 英文作者\\n\\n* [lilco